<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.7">
<l>aṉṉaiyu mattaṉumeṉ ṟaṭiyōmuk kiraṅkiṟṟilaḷ</l>
<l>piṉṉaitaṉ kātalaṉṟaṉ peruntōḷnalam pēṇiṉaḷāl</l>
<l>miṉṉaiyum vañciyaiyumveṉ ṟilaṅkumiṭai yāḷnaṭantu</l>
<l>puṉṉaiyu maṉṉamumcūḻ puṉalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She has no pity for us who are devoted [to her]</l>
<l rend="indent">not calling “mother and father”;</l>
<l>She absolutely cherished the beauty of the broad shoulders</l>
<l rend="indent">of the beloved of Piṉṉai.</l>
<l>[As] she, with a waist that shines, rivaling [both] lightning and vañci creepers, walks,</l>
<l>Are they setting out for Āli, its waters encircled by laurel trees and swans?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
